1
00:00:00,180 --> 00:00:03,060
[Episode 2]

2
00:00:00,180 --> 00:00:00,180
[Pattaya Jazz Bar]

3
00:00:09,940 --> 00:00:11,820
[Drew
Bin's good friend]

4
00:00:15,630 --> 00:00:18,190
Holy crap!

5
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:22,630
Did you get plastic surgery
or a body transplant?

6
00:00:22,910 --> 00:00:24,350
I almost didn't recognize you.

7
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,790
You're exaggerating.

8
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:27,110
[Wu
Drew's friend, Animal Party]

9
00:00:27,110 --> 00:00:29,190
Hey, who's this, Drew?

10
00:00:29,190 --> 00:00:29,380
Introduce us, will you?

11
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:30,500
[Rod
Drew's friend, Wu's bedmate]

12
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,190
This is Wu and Rod,
my college friends.

13
00:00:34,220 --> 00:00:36,910
This is Bin,
my middle school classmate.

14
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:38,260
Hello.

15
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:42,980
Is he your friend
or your sandwich partner?

16
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:45,150
Wanna taste?

17
00:00:45,180 --> 00:00:47,670
The filling in the middle is packed tight.

18
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:50,510
The mayo is also very thick.

19
00:00:51,310 --> 00:00:52,870
And incredibly sweet too.

20
00:00:53,270 --> 00:00:55,350
Hmm, oh my!

21
00:00:55,830 --> 00:00:56,980
The real deal.

22
00:00:59,310 --> 00:01:01,470
Hey Rod, we've got business.

23
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:04,069
-We'll be back later.
-Hmm.

24
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:10,740
Wait here.
I'll get you a drink.

25
00:01:10,780 --> 00:01:11,740
Okay.

26
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:17,380
I'm coming, bro.

27
00:01:18,780 --> 00:01:20,500
[Jane, now]
[Taehyung, now]

28
00:01:20,810 --> 00:01:23,690
Hey, is that the new guy?

29
00:01:24,810 --> 00:01:26,690
The one who came with Drew?

30
00:01:28,210 --> 00:01:31,570
Hey, remember those two?

31
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:42,539
Hahaha.

32
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:50,710
Those little brats who used to bully me.

33
00:01:51,509 --> 00:01:53,870
Of course I remember their faces.

34
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:58,020
Let's go.
I don't want trouble.

35
00:01:58,060 --> 00:02:00,310
No need. Just watch.

36
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:02,060
They'll come to me.

37
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:08,419
3

38
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:09,470
2

39
00:02:09,699 --> 00:02:10,340
1

40
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:15,430
Drew!

41
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:16,870
Is this your friend?

42
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:18,860
Can I pursue him?

43
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:19,900
Is he single?

44
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:27,220
[Max
Bar owner, Mafia]

45
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:33,280
[To be continued]
